rows.label: tlk45350351_01_msg0001
rows.name:
There aren't any ships leaving
for Acedia for a fair while.

rows.label: tlk45350351_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You'll bore yourselves to death if you
hang around here, so I'd suggest paying
the capital a visit.

rows.label: tlk45350351_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Just head out of Port Ananyam
and follow the path straight.
